commit.message:
ISOTPScan improvement (#2777)

* This PR changes the internal behaviour of the ISOTPScan functions.

The captured noise before a scan is executed is now used to suppress probe packets.
On some cars these probe packets caused errors. This change ensures that no packets
which could interfeer with the cars internal communication are sent during an ISOTP
scan.

Cleanup of function comments and added type informations

* Add unit tests

* This PR changes the internal behaviour of the ISOTPScan functions.

which could interfeer with the cars internal communication are sent during an ISOTP
scan.
